 <H1>Abstraction</H1> 
 <P><H2>Abstraction</H2>
</P>
<P><UL><LI>Identifying important aspects while ignoring details (separating important concerns)<LI>Abstraction permeates software development<UL><LI>From natural language descriptions to mathematical models<LI>From requirements to code<UL><LI>one specification but many realizations</UL><LI>From products to process</UL><LI>Models are abstractions of reality<UL><LI>Abstraction depends on purpose or point of view</UL></UL></P>
